Title: Conjured Help
Description:
If you're looking for food--softy food--I'm afraid we're clean out. Nothing but good ol' rocks and gems here at the moment.

It's starting to become a problem, actually.

Say... you wouldn't be able to do anything about that, would you? Rustle us up some victuals for the fleshy folk?
ObjectivesText: Summon food for Innkeeper Brax in the Gundargaz Inn.

Objectives.Text: Bring Innkeeper Brax 80 Conjured Mana Buns
